    <abstract id="aspace_2940c3ff1b17004a8cf682ff0cae256f">This collection consists of scrapbooks, invitations, awards, and correspondence documenting Solis Horwitz's work within the federal government, 1945-1971. Horwitz was a University of Pittsburgh alumni and professor from 1968-1972.</abstract>
